#- 1 West Avenue,
Tigerstaden.
The holder of this deed is the owner of this property.
If you lose your deed, you'll have no way of proving your ownership.
You own 1 West Avenue from level 1 to level 256.
When you're selling
#- this property, give this deed to the new owner.
